{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|とし}}
/to{{sub|2}}si/}} → /tosi/ → /toɕi/

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=とし}}. Originally referred to [[grain]], particularly [[rice]], and by extension, the year's [[harvest]].<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref>

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|とせ}}
/to{{sub|2}}se/ → /tose/

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-|sort=とし}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> Likely a shift in pronunciation from ''toshi''.

